Ensure python is installed for your system



Setup a python virtual environment:
Ubuntu:
python -m venv /path/to/new/virtual/environment

Windows:
python -m venv C:\path\to\new\virtual\environment



Navigate to environment directory and activate it:
Ubuntu:
source venv/bin/activate

Windows:
.\Scripts\activate



Navigate to the webserver python file "app.py" and run it:
python[3] app.py


This will output a URL to a locally hosted webserver
Copy and Paste that URL into a browser and enjoy